    dc:creator "Soisook, Pipat; Sribuarod, Kriangsak; Karapan, Sunate; Safoowong, Mongkol; Billasoy, Sawwalak; Thong, Vu Dinh; Chang, Yang; Gong, Lixin; Lin, Aiqing; Sztencel-Jabłonka, Anna; Bogdanowicz, Wiesław; Bates, Paul J. J." ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "The first record of Ia io Thomas, 1902 (Mammalia: Chiroptera: Vespertilionidae) from the Sundaic Subregion, with a description of a new subspecies from peninsular Thailand" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043800>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043802>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043804>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043806>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043808>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043810>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043798> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043800>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ia io peninsulata subsp. nov., PSUZC-MM 2012.159 (paratype), female, from peninsular Thailand. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043800/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043802>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Comparison of the cranial and dental characters between (a) I. io peninsulata subsp. nov., PSUZC-MM 2012.158 (holotype), male, from peninsular Thailand, and (b) I. io io BMNH. 2.6.10.2 (holotype), male, from China. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043802/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043804>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal (left) and ventral view (right) of the baculum of I. io peninsulata subsp. nov., PSUZC-MM 2012.158 (holotype), male, from peninsular Thailand. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043804/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043806>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Biplot between skull length and maxillary toothrow length of I. io peninsulata subsp. nov. and I. io io." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043806/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043808>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Principal component analysis based on 12 craniodental measurements of I. io peninsulata subsp. nov. and I. io io. Factor loading scores are in table 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043810>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Bayesian tree using HKY + I + G nucleotide substitution model based on the mitochondrial COI gene of Ia io and other vespertilionids as outgroup. The node labels indicate posterior probability values. Samples included in this analysis are listed in Appendix." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043810/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1043798>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map of the localities of specimens of Ia io analysed in this study; black dots = specimens examined for morphological analysis only; red dots = specimens used for genetic analysis only; half black / red dots = specimens used for both morphological and genetic analyses. Type localities of the nominate subspecies io and the new subspecies peninsulata, as well as the other two synonyms, Ia longimana and Parascotomanes beaulieui, are indicated. The grey shaded area is the known distribution of Ia io based on data in the IUCN Red List." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1043798/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

